text: Had interview with Accenture:  Interviewer was 18 years of experience  She asked : suppose you are working with banking client and Clint given you a business problem , and refused to give any data for modeling  I asked we can ask for simulation of data.  She said no they are not ready to share a single feature data , now proceed with modeling.  I said really , I how can I make model without data  She said these are the real scenario. tell me how will you do..  And on the basis of this she rejected me .
